{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/extras/SteamGif2.gif?t=1738132219\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Always on is an interactive short story that can be played through in roughly 1 hour. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as Leya, an AI assistant to the 7 year old Evie. This little girl will test your abilities as well as your boundaries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/extras/what_kind_of_bot_will_you_be.png?t=1738132219\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/extras/SteamGifEyes.gif?t=1738132219\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/extras/theme.png?t=1738132219\" />On a deeper level Always On is a story about the concept of Alignment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alignment is what AI developers do to ensure AI systems act in accordance with human values. This seems like it is a technical problem, but it is also fundamentally a philosophical one. Because if we as humans can\u2019t agree on ethical questions? How are we going to align an AI that is smarter than us? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/extras/choices_matter.png?t=1738132219\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/extras/ChoosingGif.gif?t=1738132219\" />All choices you make in the game change your &quot;alignment&quot; which alters the route you take in the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are 4 major endings, replay the game to see all of them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/extras/Visual_Novel.png?t=1738132219\" />Yes. Although it's not a typical visual novel I would still classify it as a short visual novel. The art style is heavily influenced by comic books.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/extras/About_this_game_evie_heart.png?t=1738132219\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Out of love","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3087090/9867f9bdef4ebb8a192fb2e896bbd0a606e4bef6.jpg"},{"name":"We know what's best","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3087090/fbe1f87d3f18ba4537c37aad3ffa5af5f89390df.jpg"},{"name":"I'm there","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3087090/a094296aa3ad425615b4b8c7787e21e701c5a511.jpg"},{"name":"My life is my own","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3087090/1fb99c6e7d0b34ce7f43f74df656a8df26a45a0c.jpg"},{"name":"Psycho","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3087090/9b3e1f57d024366ccf28f152466f82b8fde266d0.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738132219","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/page.bg.jpg?t=1738132219","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738132219","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3087090/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738132219","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id